These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, november
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, social-worker
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, volleyball
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, scientific
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
3. the designer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Birthday       | november       | december |
| Job         | social-worker | designer  |
| Sport       | volleyball    | soccer    |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific       | documentary      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade
2 different games are played: go, domino
There 2 different types of food: pineapple, cucumber
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, surfing
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person playing go is on the far left##1
3. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | almond-milk |
| Game           | go | domino      |
| Food   | cucumber  | pineapple      |
| Sport         | snowboarding | surfing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
2 different games are played: whist, chess
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, country
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, alhambra
1. the fan of country is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the alhambra-smoker##1
3. the person playing whist is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | soy-milk  |
| Game          | whist    | chess   |
| Music-Genre   | country  | ambient   |
| Cigar     | alhambra     | game |

