.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
There 2 different types of food: lemon, papaya
2 different pets are kept: frog, hedgehog
House: craftsman, modern
1. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | soy-milk |
| Food          | papaya         | lemon    |
| Pet           | hedgehog | frog    |
| House   | craftsman           | modern   |

