The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, november
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Pet           | guinea-pig  | goldfish   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | salsa      |
| Sport         | climbing | volleyball |
| Birthday     | november     | february |

