.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
House: art-deco, futuristic
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, superhero
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, pakistani
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, van
1. the art-deco house is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the art-deco house is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the nigerian is the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| House           | futuristic | art-deco     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime          | superhero |
| Nationality           | nigerian          | pakistani    |
| Transport     | van            | bus       |

 